<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='428562' id='t-428562'>Just listen to the sound for a moment.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='433236' id='t-433236'>Shhhhhhhhhh.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='439228' id='t-439228'>Okay, nothing very interesting.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='441293' id='t-441293'>Now, listen to what happens
